Chef May.

519
00:41:26,063 --> 00:41:26,856
Ai!

520
00:41:26,905 --> 00:41:27,482
Chef May.

521
00:41:27,548 --> 00:41:28,795
Stop it right now.

522
00:41:28,940 --> 00:41:30,471
Here. Feed me.

523
00:41:30,608 --> 00:41:32,248
I’ll see if it’s as yummy as you claimed.

524
00:41:32,650 --> 00:41:35,837
