562
00:44:27,382 --> 00:44:29,320
Maybe your dad misses you.

563
00:44:31,631 --> 00:44:32,631
No way.

564
00:44:36,010 --> 00:44:37,232
For someone like him,

565
00:44:38,422 --> 00:44:40,232
