599
00:46:44,531 --> 00:46:45,576
Tell her to come inside.

600
00:46:59,308 --> 00:46:59,915
Mom.

601
00:47:00,195 --> 00:47:01,195
Hm?

602
00:47:01,930 --> 00:47:03,179
